Package: rigakuXRD
Type: Package
Title: X-Ray Diffraction Data Analysis Package for Rigaku Data Sets
Version: 0.3.1
Year: 2024
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Gredig", email = "thomas.gredig@csulb.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5824-7626"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <thomas.gredig@csulb.edu>
Description: Imports x-ray diffractometer (XRD) data and
  assists with the x-ray data analysis. It supports ASC, RAS, RASX, and TXT
  data files for import and provides tools to find / fit XRD peaks.
URL: https://thomasgredig.github.io/rigakuXRD/, https://github.com/thomasgredig/rigakuXRD
License: GPL (>= 3)
